OL,3,CCouncil defends contractors wearing
OL,4,Cbalaclavas to remove flags from
OL,5,Clampposts
OL,7,FA council has defended sending in
OL,8,Fteams dressed in balaclavas to take
OL,9,Fdown flags from lampposts - claiming
OL,10,Fworkers have been subjected to
OL,11,F"organised harassment and
OL,12,Fintimidation".
OL,14,FIn a series of videos widely shared on
OL,15,Fsocial media, masked workmen have been
OL,16,Fseen taking down St George's Cross and
OL,17,FUnion flags put up across York.
