OL,7,FThe move has been criticised as heavy
OL,8,Fhanded and distressing by some - but
OL,9,FYork City Council said on Monday (1
OL,10,FDecember) that the approach was
OL,11,Fnecessary after staff and contractors
OL,12,Fhad been seriously threatened in
OL,13,Fperson and online.
OL,15,FA spokesperson for the authority said:
OL,16,F"Contractors wearing face coverings is
OL,17,Fabout us allowing them to protect
OL,18,Ftheir own individual identities.
