OL,7,F"The activity of those opposed to the
OL,8,Fremoval of the flags and threats to
OL,9,Fdate provide more than enough evidence
OL,10,Fof a significant risk to individuals'
OL,11,Fsafety.
OL,13,F"We know people creating online
OL,14,Fcontent about these workers are
OL,15,Factively trying to identify them.
OL,16,FMultiple incidents have been reported
OL,17,Fto the police.
