OL,7,F"Good progress has been made on
OL,8,Fremoving flags and they only exist in
OL,9,Fa few small pockets across the city.
OL,10,FWork to remove them is ongoing."
OL,12,FGrassroots campaign Operation Raise
OL,13,Fthe Colours was launched in August
OL,14,Fthis year in a move which saw calls
OL,15,Ffor the prominent display of Union and
OL,16,FEnglish flags across the country.
