OL,3,CCouncil defends contractors wearing
OL,4,Cbalaclavas to remove flags from
OL,5,Clampposts
OL,7,FOne of the organisations that said it
OL,8,Fwas involved in putting up the flags
OL,9,Fin York is called Flag Force UK. There
OL,10,Fis no suggestion members of the group
OL,11,Fare behind the threats and
OL,12,Fintimidation claimed to have been
OL,13,Fdirected at council workers.
OL,15,FIn a statement, Flag Force UK
OL,16,Fchallenged the validity of claims of
OL,17,Fthreats and intimidation saying
OL,18,Finstead the men deployed into
OL,19,Fneighbourhood streets had caused
OL,20,Fdistress and intimidation.
