OL,3,CCouncil defends contractors wearing
OL,4,Cbalaclavas to remove flags from
OL,5,Clampposts
OL,7,FThe group also firmly criticised the
OL,8,Fcouncil for paying masked men to
OL,9,Foperate on residential streets without
OL,10,Fdisplaying their identity.
OL,12,FThe council has previously said it
OL,13,Ftook the decision to remove the flags
OL,14,Fover concerns they were causing
OL,15,Fdivision and fear.
OL,17,FLast month it was revealed the Labour-
OL,18,Frun council had spent #16,378 removing
OL,19,Funauthorised Union and St George's
OL,20,FCross flags down from lampposts and
OL,21,Fother public places in the city.
